      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. DESPICABLE MARGO has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (17.84) last time in a Grade 5 at Richmond Straight. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Can discover winning form. 4. CAWDOR was a strong winner (19.27) from box 4 last time, scoring by 2.5 lengths at Bulli. Will need some luck early after drawing a tricky box here. The form out of last race has been strong. Expecting another bold showing. 2. PAY PAY PAY missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Mix 3/4 three back before a placing at Bulli the following run. Can turn it around this time. 3. KAYCEE TRACEY is always hard to beat when she races at this trip.\",\"runners\":[1,4,2,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
